{Speech 3}{}{Реддинг? Мы как раз туда сейчас и едем. Готов@sex@||а|?}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{Поехали!}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit*}{}{Я передумал@sex@||а| - доберусь сам@sex@||а|.}

[Text engl]
{Name}{}{Driver}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see a driver.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{A happy guy hanging a pair of keys in his arm. There are multiple lubricant spots on his armor.}
{Speech 1}{}{Преддиалоговые установки}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{ }
{Speech 2}{}{@sex@|Hi, man|Hello, dear lady|. Few cars are leaving from here now. Do you want us to give you a lift? It's free.}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{Is anyone going to Redding, by chance?}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{No, thanks, I'm fine on my own.}
{Speech 3}{}{Redding? Yes, we're actually heading there right now.}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{Let's ride!}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit*}{}{I've changed my mind, I'll get there on my own.}
